# =============================================================================
# UC4 Threat-Fusion-Agent · environment template
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Filename: env.template (the dotfile name agents/uc4-threat-fusion/.env.template
# is blocked by tooling permission settings; copy to .env at deploy time).
#
# This file contains ONLY non-secret values plus OCIDs of secrets.
# The secrets themselves live in OCI Vault; the agent runtime fetches them
# at startup using the cluster's Workload Identity / Resource Principal.
#
# Copy to .env and fill the BLOCKED items before deploying.
# Anything still set to <pending> will fail Crossplane apply.
# =============================================================================

